      "text": "code.load Path=TypeProvider.dll, on error set %loadFailed% = true",
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "indent": 0,
      "comment": "Integration cut 4 (overwrite): load a DLL that re-registers an existing built-in name\n(e.g. a custom \u0060int\u0060). A subsequent value of that name resolves to the loaded CLR type\nand renders via the loaded renderer \u2014 runtime registration wins ResolveType precedence.\nThe honest-limit caveat lives in C# RuntimeTypeLoadingTests.",
